### Health check
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================
### ATHLETES
### ===========================================

### Create Participant - Athlete (Swimming, USA)
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "givenName": "Katie",
  "familyName": "Ledecky",
  "genderCode": "F",
  "birthDate": "1997-03-17",
  "organisation": "USA",
  "functions": [
    { "functionId": "ATH", "disciplineCode": "SWM", "isMain": true }
  ]
}

